<!-- Begin package Header /health/components/package-header 20536266 package-->
			<h2 id="package-title"><a href="http://www.health.com/health/package/0,,20536266,00.html" style="color:#f15922">Cold and Flu Prevention Center</a></h2>
			<div id="package-title-dek">Achoo! Follow these tips to boost your chance of staying healthy during cold and flu season&#151;or at least minimizing your downtime if you don’t. From chicken soup to natural remedies, we have you covered.</div>
	<div id="slideshowWrapper">
		<h1 id="content-title">5 Ways to Tell If You Need an Antibiotic</h1>
		<div class="dek">Physicians often use a combination of experience and science when deciding to dole out an antibiotic. Here are five things most doctors take into consideration when making that decision.</div> <div class="share">

